data.description: Downtown Weatherford historic living! This large corner lot with a 27ft front porch is perfect for rocking chairs. The turn of the century touches & metal roof welcome you into the large living with floor to ceiling brick wood burning fireplace encased by custom built ins. The open concept kitchen has bar seating, gas range, overhang cabinets, spacious adjacent dining with ample room for large table plus bar seating. The primary suite has bay windows, original wood flooring, walk in closet, and newly created barn door en suite bath with claw foot tub and vanity. This flex plan allows the third bed to also serve as a large 2nd living with window wall and direct access to the yard. Third bed has a custom bookshelf wall, walk in closet, and en suite barn door bath with walk in shower. Backyard is grand with new privacy fencing and large covered patio. Large one car garage plus 11ft tall 20x20 carport allows for plenty of covered parking. $10K New Champion Windows.
